# NYC events calendar for 2025

![Rossilynne Skena Culgan](https://media.timeout.com/images/106210735/170/170/image.jpg)

Want to know what’s happening in New York today, this weekend or in the coming months? Use our NYC events calendar 2025 as your guide to find the best fall, winter, spring and summer events. Major events to look forward to this time of year include [Valentine's date ideas](https://www.timeout.com/newyork/sex-dating/best-valentines-day-date-ideas), [Black History Month](https://www.timeout.com/newyork/black-history-month) and [St. Patrick's Day](https://www.timeout.com/newyork/things-to-do/st-patricks-day-parade-and-events-in-new-york-city?package_page=35809).

Ready to unleash your inner culture vulture? Peep our top picks for the best [museum exhibitions](https://www.timeout.com/newyork/attractions/best-museum-exhibitions-in-nyc) this year. All you need to do is buy the tickets!
